 <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
  <tr>
    <td><p align="justify">Karnataka Bank Ltd. (hereinafter called &#147;The Bank&#148;) which expression 
      shall unless repugnant to the context or meaning thereof include its successors 
      and assigns) having at the request of M/s. _______________________ (hereinafter 
      called &#147;The Borrower&#148;) agreed to grant to the borrower Foreign 
      Currency Loan facility (hereinafter called as FCL facility) on the borrower 
      agreeing to the terms and conditions hereinafter appearing.</p></td>
  </tr>
</table>
<br>
<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
  <tr>
    <td width="3%">&nbsp;</td>
    <td width="97%">WHEREAS The expression &#147;the Borrower&#148; shall when 
      the borrower is : <br> 
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="3%" valign="top">(vi) </td>
    <td width="97%">
<p align="justify">An Association corporate or incorporate include its successors 
      and assigns and all members and their respective heirs, executors, administrators 
      and assigns;</p><br> </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="3%" valign="top">(vii)</td>
    <td width="97%">
<p align="justify"> A trust, whether public or private, the trustee or trustees 
      for the time being.(ii)The Borrower is enjoying Cash Credit (Hyp) credit 
      facility hereinafter called as C.C. (H) Credit facility as mentioned in 
      Schedule A to this Agreement and has executed various security documents 
      in favour of the bank on &#133;&#133;&#133;&#133;. And created charge over 
      properties of the borrower listed in Schedule B as and by way of security 
      for securing the said credit facility and has promised to repay the outstanding 
      monies due and payable to the bank in respect of the said credit facility 
      mentioned in Schedule A together with interest thereon in Indian rupees.</p><br></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="3%" valign="top">
       
      <p>(ii) 
    </td>
    <td width="97%">
      <p></p>
      <p align="justify">Out of the C.C. (H) credit facility mentioned hereinabove a credit 
        facility in form of Working Capital Demand Loan to the extent of Rs. <b><%=Helper.correctNull((String)hshValues.get("sancamount"))%></b>/- 
        has been granted by the Bank to the Borrower.</p><br>
            </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="3%" valign="top">(ii)</td>
    <td width="97%">
<p align="justify">The Borrower has availed the said Working Capital Demand 
      Loan (hereinafter called WCDL (Credit) facility for the sake of Brevity) 
      to the extent of Rs. <b><%=Helper.correctNull((String)hshValues.get("sancamount"))%></b>/- (Rupees _______________________) out of the 
      total C.C. (H) credit facility sanctioned.</p><br></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="3%" valign="top">(ii)</td>
    <td width="97%"> 
      <p align="justify"> In terms of the RBI Credit Policy in respect of Foreign Currency 
        Loan laid down in or around ________________ the Borrower desires to avail 
        the WCDL credit facility in Foreign Currency.</p><br>
       
            </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td width="3%" valign="top">(ii)</td>
    <td width="97%">  
      <p align="justify"> The Bank agrees to allow the Borrower to avail the WCDL credit facility 
      as mentioned in Schedule &#145;A&#146; and draw the monies in respect thereof 
      in US Dollars, in terms of RBI credit policy, which will be termed as FCL 
      credit facility.</p><br></td>
  </tr><tr>
    <td width="3%" valign="top">(iii)</td>
    <td width="97%">
<p align="justify"> The Borrower has requested the Bank to modify the terms 
      and conditions of agreement of Hypothecation/pledge/mortgage executed by 
      the borrower while availing credit facilities mentioned in Schedule &#145;A&#146; 
      hereto to the extent as envisaged by these presents. </p><br></td>
  </tr>  
</table>
 
